other params

Examples

library(sf)
mtq <- st_read(system.file("geojson/mtq.geojson", package = "bertin"), quiet = TRUE)
bt_param(margin = 10, width = 500, projection = "Winkel3") |>
  bt_layer(geojson = mtq, fill = "red") |>
  bt_draw()
